snippet.title: SOVIET ANOMALY 7 PRE RELEASE TEASER
snippet.description:
SOVIET ANOMALY 7 IS A NEW GAME ON SOVIET STYLE SETTING AND PSYHOLOGICAL HORROR GENRE SIMILAR TO 'The Platform 8' and 'The Exit 8' GAMES.

ON THIS VIDEO YOU CAN SEE ANOMALY CAR ON THE ROOF SCENE.

IF YOU LIKE THIS GAME DEMO, PLEASE ADD THIS GAME TO YOUR STEAM WISH LIST.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2965940/Soviet_Anomaly_7/?beta=1
